trans-unit.source: The QuickBooks Payroll File Import Extension

seg-source.mrk: The QuickBooks Payroll File Import Extension

trans-unit.source: Use the QuickBooks Payroll File Import extension to import payroll transactions from QuickBooks to general ledger accounts in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: Use the QuickBooks Payroll File Import extension to import payroll transactions from QuickBooks to general ledger accounts in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Použijte rozšíření QuickBooks Payroll File Import pro import transakcí mezd z QuickBooks na účty hlavní knihy v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For example, this is useful when you are transitioning from QuickBooks to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], or if you outsource your payroll but also want to keep track of it in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: For example, this is useful when you are transitioning from QuickBooks to [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)], or if you outsource your payroll but also want to keep track of it in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: To je užitečné například při přechodu z QuickBooks do [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] nebo pokud zadáváte výplatu mezd externě, ale také ji chcete sledovat v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The first step is for you, or maybe your accountant, to use the export features in QuickBooks to export the payroll data to an .IIF file.

seg-source.mrk: The first step is for you, or maybe your accountant, to use the export features in QuickBooks to export the payroll data to an .IIF file.

target.mrk: Prvním krokem je, pro vás nebo vašeho účetního, použití funkcí exportu v QuickBooks k exportu mzdových dat do souboru .IIF.

trans-unit.source: The second step is to open the **General Journals** page in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] and use the **Import Payroll Transactions** action to import the file.

seg-source.mrk: The second step is to open the **General Journals** page in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] and use the **Import Payroll Transactions** action to import the file.

target.mrk: Druhým krokem je otevření stránky **Hlavní deníky** v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] a výber akce **Import mzdových transakcí** pro import souboru.

trans-unit.source: During the import process you map the general ledger accounts from QuickBooks to corresponding accounts in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

seg-source.mrk: During the import process you map the general ledger accounts from QuickBooks to corresponding accounts in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

target.mrk: Během procesu importu namapujte účty hlavní knihy z QuickBooks na odpovídající účty v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The final step is to post the payroll transactions in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] according to the account mapping.

seg-source.mrk: The final step is to post the payroll transactions in [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] according to the account mapping.

target.mrk: Posledním krokem je zaúčtování mzdových transakcí v [!INCLUDE[d365fin](includes/d365fin_md.md)] podle mapování účtů.
Pro více informací běžte na [Import mzdových transakcí](finance-how-import-payroll-transactions.md).
